# Purpose of Script

1. DROP DATABASE
→ Deletes old warehouse

2. CREATE DATABASE
→ Creates fresh warehouse

3. USE Datawarehouse
→ Selects working database

4. CREATE SCHEMA bronze
→ Raw data layer
(unprocessed source data)

5. CREATE SCHEMA silver
→ Cleaned data layer
(transformed + validated data)

6. CREATE SCHEMA gold
→ Business analytics layer
(reporting + dashboards + KPIs)

Flow:
Bronze → Silver → Gold

Meaning:
Raw Data → Clean Data → Business Insights


DROP DATABASE IF EXISTS Datawarehouse;

CREATE DATABASE Datawarehouse;

USE Datawarehouse;

CREATE SCHEMA bronze;

CREATE SCHEMA silver;

CREATE SCHEMA gold;

